The '''Army of the Wookiee Trade Guild''' was a group of [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] that defended the [[Wookiee Trade Guild]].

==History==
They fought in the [[Kashyyyk Trade Rebellion]] that took place in [[28 BBY/Legends|28 BBY]], at the beginning of the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]]. The army was completely destroyed by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation's]] [[B2-series super battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] and the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Dooku/Legends|Darth Tyranus]], who led the attack.

